Players are able to access three sea areas: 鎮守府海域, 北方泊地海域, and 南方泊地海域 when they start the game.

While some maps resemble ones from the browser edition and look identical in nature, they're essentially different maps with new enemy compositions and possibly different branching rules.

Clearing each regular map gives the player 300 strategy points. Clearing the last map of a hexagon gives 1000 strategy points and a medal.

